===============================================================================
anonymous-struct-methods
===============================================================================
Methods inside anonymous structs should still be classified as methods, not functions.
The anonymous struct provides the context that makes nested functions into methods.
lang: cpp

--- file: src/lib.cpp ---
// Anonymous struct with a method
struct {
    int value;
    int getValue() { return value; }
} instance;

// Named struct for comparison
struct Named {
    int value;
    int getValue() { return value; }
};

// Union with method
union {
    int i;
    float f;
    int getInt() { return i; }
} u;

